  "title": "Change searchParameters at runtime",
  "body": "Hello,\r\nI've an issue with instantsearch.js.\r\n\r\nI'm trying to change the value of searchParameters.distinct at runtime but the search results is broken.\r\n\r\nHow can I change the parameter at runtime? Perhaps instantsearch exposes some method?\r\n\r\n\r\nThis i my code:\r\n\r\n**Algolia**\r\n```\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n    appId: APPID,\r\n    apiKey: APIKEY,\r\n    indexName: 'products',\r\n    urlSync: true,\r\n    searchParameters: {\r\n        distinct: true\r\n    }\r\n});\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n    instantsearch.widgets.hits({\r\n        container: '#products',\r\n        templates: {\r\n            item: getTemplate('product'),\r\n            empty: getTemplate('no-results')\r\n        }\r\n    })\r\n);\r\n\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n    instantsearch.widgets.refinementList({\r\n        container: '#facet_cat_color',\r\n        attributeName: 'cat_color',\r\n        sortBy: ['isRefined', 'count:desc', 'name:asc'],\r\n        operator: 'or'\r\n);\r\nsearch.start();\r\n```\r\n\r\n**App**\r\n```\r\n$('#products-list').delegate('#facet_cat_color .ais-refinement-list--item', 'click', function() {\r\n    if ($('#facet_cat_color .ais-refinement-list--item.ais-refinement-list--item__active').length) {\r\n        search.helper.state.distinct = false;\r\n    } else {\r\n        search.helper.state.distinct = true;\r\n    }\r\n    search.start();\r\n});\r\n\r\n```\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\nChange the search parameter\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- instantsearch.js\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\ninstantsearch.js 1.11.2\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThanks\r\n",
